ygData.subject: Re: Crisson's Pixie Chase
ygData.msgSnippet: Friend of mine was saying that the song was being noted as Pixie Strike when he first got it. When played it would do 1 dmg to the target much like a pixie
ygData.messageBody:
Friend of mine was saying that the song was being noted as Pixie Strike
when he first got it. When played it would do 1 dmg to the target much like
a pixie (maybe poison in there then). It was then 'fixed' to do the
mesmerize that is occurring today.

Is this what you were referring to?

Good Journey,

Sineras Silverlyre (Cazic-Thule)

8)It is a targeted Lullaby song. It is very useful when your group is
8)fighting 2 yellow mobs, it let you sleep one while your group is
8)concentrating on the other. I think they also change the
8)song name from
8)Pixie Chase to Pixie.. something else.
8)
8)And to the other person who was asking about the level 3
8)song. It is NOT a
8)mana regen song, it regen STA not mana. To get the mana
8)regen song, you
8)will have to wait until level 32. The message will say your
8)mind is clear..
8)when you play that song.
8)
8)>
8)>Does anyone know what Crisson's Pixie Chase does? It is the
8)lvl 28 song
8)>and
8)>I heard it was tweaked on the patch before the last one,
8)still don't know
8)>what it does though.
